    java.lang.Cloneable, Node, TreePrinterNode
    class Branch
extends java.lang.Object
implements Node, java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents a branch of a CnfGrammar i.e. (A)->(B)(C) or (A)->(B)c or (A)->bc
